<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>NGold — भारत गोल्ड इंटेलिजेंस</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/Chart.js/4.4.1/chart.umd.min.js"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Hind:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg0:#04030A;--bg1:#0A0812;--bg2:#11101C;--bg3:#181628;--bg4:#211F32;
  --bd1:#1C1A2E;--bd2:#2A2840;--bd3:#403C60;
  --g100:#FFE566;--g200:#F5C518;--g300:#D4A017;--g400:#9A6F08;--g500:#5C3D05;
  --up:#00E87A;--upbg:rgba(0,232,122,.1);--upbd:rgba(0,232,122,.25);
  --dn:#FF4D6D;--dnbg:rgba(255,77,109,.1);--dnbd:rgba(255,77,109,.25);
  --bl:#7B8CFF;--blbg:rgba(123,140,255,.1);--blbd:rgba(123,140,255,.25);
  --or:#FF9F43;--saffron:#FF9933;--indiagreen:#138808;
  --sv:#C8D4E8;
  --tx0:#FFFFFF;--tx1:#EDE8F8;--tx2:#B0A8CC;--tx3:#7068A0;--tx4:#3D3860;
  --glow-g:0 0 40px rgba(245,197,24,.2),0 0 80px rgba(245,197,24,.07);
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--bg1);color:var(--tx1);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;min-height:100vh;overflow-x:hidden}
body::before{content:'';position:fixed;top:-200px;right:-100px;width:600px;height:600px;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(245,197,24,.06),transparent 65%);
  pointer-events:none;z-index:0;animation:amb 9s ease-in-out infinite}
body::after{content:'';position:fixed;bottom:-200px;left:-100px;width:500px;height:500px;
  background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(123,140,255,.04),transparent 65%);pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
@keyframes amb{0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}50%{opacity:.5;transform:scale(1.15)}}
.wrap{max-width:1340px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 18px;position:relative;z-index:1}

.ticker{width:100%;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg0);border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd1);padding:7px 0;position:relative}
.ticker::before,.ticker::after{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;width:80px;height:100%;z-index:2}
.ticker::before{left:0;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--bg0),transparent)}
.ticker::after{right:0;background:linear-gradient(270deg,var(--bg0),transparent)}
.ticker-inner{display:flex;width:max-content;animation:tick 32s linear infinite}
@keyframes tick{0%{transform:translateX(0)}100%{transform:translateX(-50%)}}
.ti{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;padding:0 22px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;white-space:nowrap;border-right:1px solid var(--bd1)}
.ti .n{color:var(--tx3);letter-spacing:1px}.ti .v{color:var(--tx0);font-weight:500}
.ti .c.up{color:var(--up)}.ti .c.dn{color:var(--dn)}.ti .c.st{color:var(--tx3)}

.india-stripe{height:3px;display:flex}
.india-stripe div{flex:1}
.india-stripe .s1{background:var(--saffron)}.india-stripe .s2{background:#fff}.india-stripe .s3{background:var(--indiagreen)}

header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 18px;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd1);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:200;
  background:rgba(10,8,18,.94);backdrop-filter:blur(20px)}
.brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px}
.ico{width:36px;height:36px;border-radius:9px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--g200),var(--g400));
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:16px;
  box-shadow:var(--glow-g);animation:icoPulse 3s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes icoPulse{0%,100%{box-shadow:var(--glow-g)}50%{box-shadow:0 0 60px rgba(245,197,24,.35),0 0 100px rgba(245,197,24,.12)}}
.bname{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:25px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1px;
  background:linear-gradient(110deg,#FFE566,#F5C518,#D4A017,#F5C518);
  background-size:200% auto;-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
  animation:shine 4s linear infinite}
@keyframes shine{0%{background-position:0% center}100%{background-position:200% center}}
.bsub{font-family:'Hind',sans-serif;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--tx3);display:block;margin-top:-2px}
.lr{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px}
.lring{position:relative;width:9px;height:9px}
.lring::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;border-radius:50%;background:var(--up);animation:ring 1.4s ease-out infinite}
.lring::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:2px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--up)}
@keyframes ring{0%{transform:scale(1);opacity:.8}100%{transform:scale(2.8);opacity:0}}
.lt{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--up);letter-spacing:1px}
#clk{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--tx2);margin-left:4px}
.hr{display:flex;gap:7px}
.btn{border:none;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:10px;
  padding:7px 14px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;letter-spacing:.4px}
.bg{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--g300),var(--g200));color:#05040A}
.bg:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(245,197,24,.3)}
.bgh{background:transparent;border:1px solid var(--bd2);color:var(--tx2)}
.bgh:hover{border-color:var(--bd3);color:var(--tx1)}

#sb{background:var(--bg0);border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd1);padding:6px 18px;
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.ok{color:var(--up)}.er{color:var(--dn)}.ld{color:var(--g200)}

/* WHY-NO-TODAY EXPLAINER BANNER */
.explain-banner{background:rgba(123,140,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(123,140,255,.2);
  border-radius:14px;padding:16px 20px;margin:18px 0;display:flex;gap:14px;align-items:flex-start;
  animation:fadeUp .5s ease both}
.explain-icon{font-size:24px;flex-shrink:0}
.explain-text{font-size:11px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.7}
.explain-text strong{color:var(--bl)}
.explain-text code{background:var(--bg3);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:4px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px}

#sourcePanel{display:none;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bd2);
  border-radius:14px;padding:18px;margin:18px 0;animation:fadeIn .3s ease;font-size:11px}
.src-title{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(--g200)}
.src-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:7px 10px;background:var(--bg3);
  border-radius:7px;margin-bottom:6px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;gap:10px}
.src-row .sn{color:var(--tx2)}.src-row .su{color:var(--bl);text-align:right}

.sec{padding-top:26px}
.sh{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px}
.sl{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.sn2{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--g300);
  background:rgba(245,197,24,.07);border:1px solid rgba(245,197,24,.15);
  padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;letter-spacing:1px}
.st{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;color:var(--tx0)}
.ss{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-top:2px}
.tabs{display:flex;gap:2px;background:var(--bg0);border:1px solid var(--bd1);border-radius:8px;padding:3px}
.tab{padding:5px 13px;border-radius:6px;font-size:10px;cursor:pointer;color:var(--tx3);
  border:none;background:none;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;transition:all .2s}
.tab.on{background:var(--bg4);color:var(--g200);font-weight:500}

.culture-banner{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(255,153,51,.06),rgba(19,136,8,.06));
  border:1px solid var(--bd2);border-radius:14px;padding:16px 20px;margin-bottom:18px;
  display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;animation:fadeUp .5s ease both}
.culture-icon{font-size:28px;flex-shrink:0}
.culture-text{font-size:11px;color:var(--tx2);line-height:1.6;font-family:'Hind',sans-serif}
.culture-text strong{color:var(--g200)}

.pred-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:22px}
.pred-card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bd2);border-radius:16px;
  padding:20px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:transform .3s,border-color .3s;
  animation:fadeUp .5s ease both}
.pred-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);border-color:var(--bd3)}
.pred-card.bull::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--up),transparent)}
.pred-card.bear::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--dn),transparent)}
.pglow{position:absolute;top:-50px;right:-50px;width:160px;height:160px;border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;opacity:.05}
.bull .pglow{background:var(--up)}.bear .pglow{background:var(--dn)}
.pred-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:4px}
.pred-eye{font-size:8px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}
.pred-label{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;margin-top:4px;margin-bottom:2px}
.conf{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:20px;
  background:rgba(245,197,24,.07);color:var(--g200);border:1px solid rgba(245,197,24,.18)}
.pred-note{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:12px;
  padding:8px 10px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:8px;line-height:1.6}
.pred-rows{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px}
.pred-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
  padding:8px 12px;background:var(--bg3);border-radius:9px;border:1px solid var(--bd1);transition:background .2s}
.pred-row:hover{background:var(--bg4)}
.pred-when{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;min-width:68px}
.pv1{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--g200)}
.pv1 em{font-style:normal;font-size:8px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}
.pv8{font-size:8px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-top:1px}
.dir-chip{font-size:9px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:7px;font-weight:500}
.dir-chip.up{color:var(--up);background:var(--upbg);border:1px solid var(--upbd)}
.dir-chip.dn{color:var(--dn);background:var(--dnbg);border:1px solid var(--dnbd)}

.rg{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px}
.rc{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bd2);border-radius:15px;padding:18px 16px;
  position:relative;overflow:hidden;transition:transform .25s,border-color .25s,box-shadow .25s;
  animation:fadeUp .45s ease both}
.rc:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);border-color:var(--bd3);box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.5)}
.rc.feat{grid-column:span 2;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#0E0C1C,#161428);border-color:var(--g500)}
.rc.feat::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1.5px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--g200),var(--g300),transparent)}
.rc::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;right:0;width:100px;height:100px;
  background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(245,197,24,.04),transparent 70%);pointer-events:none}
.rc-kt{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--g400);margin-bottom:4px}
.rc-eye{font-size:8px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:8px}
.rc-rate{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:38px;font-weight:800;color:var(--g100);
  line-height:1;margin-bottom:2px;letter-spacing:-1.5px;text-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(255,229,102,.12)}
.rc:not(.feat) .rc-rate{font-size:26px}
.rc-unit{font-size:8px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:11px}
.badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-size:11px;
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:500}
.badge.up{color:var(--up);background:var(--upbg);border:1px solid var(--upbd)}
.badge.dn{color:var(--dn);background:var(--dnbg);border:1px solid var(--dnbd)}
.badge.st{color:var(--bl);background:var(--blbg)}
.rc-rng{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-top:11px;padding-top:9px;
  border-top:1px solid var(--bd1);font-size:8px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}
.rc-rng span{display:block;color:var(--tx1);font-size:11px;margin-top:2px;font-weight:500}
.rc-src{font-size:7px;color:var(--tx4);margin-top:6px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}

.usb{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--bg2),var(--bg3));border:1px solid var(--bd2);
  border-radius:15px;padding:16px 20px;display:flex;align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:22px;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:14px}
.usb-eye{font-size:8px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:4px}
.usb-price{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:34px;font-weight:800;color:var(--sv);letter-spacing:-1px}
.usb-sub{font-size:8px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}
.usb-stats{display:flex;gap:18px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.us-stat .l{font-size:8px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tx4);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:3px}
.us-stat .v{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--tx1)}
.us-stat .v.up{color:var(--up)}.us-stat .v.dn{color:var(--dn)}.us-stat .v.gl{color:var(--g200)}

.ig{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:10px;margin-bottom:22px}
.ic{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bd1);border-radius:12px;padding:13px;transition:border-color .2s,transform .2s}
.ic:hover{border-color:var(--bd3);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.ic-l{font-size:8px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tx4);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:5px}
.ic-v{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--tx0);margin-bottom:3px}
.ic-c{font-size:9px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}
.ic-n{font-size:8px;color:var(--tx4);margin-top:3px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}

.cg{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-bottom:22px}
.cc{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bd1);border-radius:15px;padding:18px;animation:fadeIn .8s ease both}
.cc.full{grid-column:span 2}
.cc-eye{font-size:8px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:2px}
.cc-val{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:21px;font-weight:700;color:var(--g200);margin-bottom:13px;letter-spacing:-.5px}
.cw{position:relative;height:190px}.cw.tall{height:265px}
.lgd{display:flex;gap:11px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:10px}
.li{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}
.ld{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0}

.tw{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bd1);border-radius:15px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:22px}
.ts{overflow-x:auto;max-height:340px;overflow-y:auto}
.ts::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px;height:4px}
.ts::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--bg3)}
.ts::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--bd3);border-radius:4px}
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;min-width:480px}
thead{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:5}
th{font-size:8px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--tx3);
  padding:11px 15px;text-align:left;background:var(--bg3);border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd2);
  font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-weight:500;white-space:nowrap}
td{padding:9px 15px;font-size:11px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd1);color:var(--tx1);white-space:nowrap;transition:background .15s}
tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
tbody tr:hover td{background:var(--bg3)}
.src-cell{font-size:8px;color:var(--tx4)}

.fest-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(150px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-bottom:22px}
.fest-card{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bd1);border-radius:12px;padding:13px;transition:border-color .2s,transform .2s}
.fest-card:hover{border-color:var(--saffron);transform:translateY(-2px)}
.fest-icon{font-size:20px;margin-bottom:6px}
.fest-name{font-family:'Hind',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:var(--tx0);margin-bottom:2px}
.fest-date{font-size:9px;color:var(--tx3);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;margin-bottom:4px}
.fest-tag{font-size:8px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:5px;background:rgba(255,153,51,.1);color:var(--saffron);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}

.div{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--bd1);margin:26px 0;position:relative}
.div::after{content:'◆';position:absolute;left:50%;top:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
  background:var(--bg1);padding:0 10px;color:var(--tx4);font-size:8px}

@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(14px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}
@keyframes flip{0%{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}40%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-6px)}60%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px)}100%{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
.flip{animation:flip .35s ease}
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px);transition:opacity .6s ease,transform .6s ease}
.reveal.vis{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}

footer{border-top:1px solid var(--bd1);padding:16px;text-align:center;
  font-size:9px;color:var(--tx4);letter-spacing:.5px;line-height:2;margin-top:26px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace}
footer strong{color:var(--tx3)}
footer .disc{color:var(--dn);font-weight:600}

@media(max-width:900px){.cg,.pred-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.cc.full{grid-column:span 1}}
@media(max-width:820px){
  .rg{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.rc.feat{grid-column:span 2}
  .ig{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}
  .usb{flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start}
}
@media(max-width:580px){
  .rg{grid-template-columns:1fr}.rc.feat{grid-column:span 1}
  .ig{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
  .rc-rate{font-size:30px!important}
  #clk,.lr{display:none}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="india-stripe"><div class="s1"></div><div class="s2"></div><div class="s3"></div></div>
<div class="ticker"><div class="ticker-inner" id="tkr"></div></div>

<header>
  <div class="brand">
    <div class="ico">✦</div>
    <div><div class="bname">NGold</div><span class="bsub">भारत का सोना · India's Gold Intelligence</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="lr"><div class="lring"></div><span class="lt">LIVE</span><span id="clk"></span></div>
  <div class="hr">
    <button class="btn bgh" onclick="toggleSources()">📋 Sources</button>
    <button class="btn bgh" onclick="animRefresh()">⟳ Refresh</button>
  </div>
</header>

<div id="sb">
  <span id="sMsg" class="ok">✓ Real data — day-wise through Jun 29, 2026 · Goodreturns news articles · PolicyBazaar · IBJA</span>
  <span id="sTime" style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--tx3)"></span>
</div>

<div class="wrap">

  <!-- WHY NO JUN 30 EXPLAINER -->
  <div class="explain-banner reveal">
    <div class="explain-icon">ℹ️</div>
    <div class="explain-text">
      <strong>Why does data stop at Jun 29, not Jun 30?</strong> Two real constraints: (1) This page runs in a browser sandbox that
      <strong>cannot make live API calls</strong> — every number here was manually verified via web search, not fetched automatically.
      (2) Jewellers (Tanishq, Kalyan, Malabar) publish each day's rate progressively through the morning — at the time of this search,
      no outlet had yet published a dated <code>Jun 30, 2026</code> article. The most recent <em>confirmed, dated</em> rate is Jun 29.
      Share today's rate with me anytime and I'll rebuild this page with it added.
    </div>
  </div>

